          MODULE=gsubedit
         VERSION=0.3
          SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$MODULE-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=$SFORGE_URL/gsubedit/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://gsubedit.sourceforge.net/index.html
         ENTERED=20020303
         UPDATED=20020310
           SHORT="DivX Subtitles Editor for Gnome"
cat << EOF
GSubEdit, or GNOME Subtitle Editor, is a tool for editing and converting DivX ;-) 
subtitles. It currently features read/write of SubRip (.srt) and MicroDVD (.sub) 
subtitles. Framerate conversion and frame displacement (Increase/decrease all frames 
by a given offset) is also supported.
EOF

